@startuml QuebracabecaProjetoAcervoDigital
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5

rectangle "PECA 1\nReact + React DOM\n(Nucleo)" as p1 #FF6B6B

rectangle "PECA 2\nReact Router\n(Navegacao)" as p2 #4ECDC4

rectangle "PECA 3\nComponentes\n(Interface)" as p3 #95E1D3

rectangle "PECA 4\nAuthContext\n(Estado Global)" as p4 #FFE66D

rectangle "PECA 5\nServicos\n(Logica)" as p5 #A8E6CF

rectangle "PECA 6\nFerramentas\n(Infraestrutura)" as p6 #C7CEEA

p1 --> p2 : encaixa com
p2 --> p3 : ativa
p3 --> p4 : usa
p4 --> p5 : chama
p5 --> p1 : alimenta

p6 -.-> p1 : compila

note right of p1
React eh a peca central!
end note

@enduml
